   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### 3.3.2 Normalize daily weather index and numeric schema\n",
    "Build a daily weather table keyed by `date` and convert weather features to numeric."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
