  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 4.3 Concatenate and sort chronologically\n",
    "Build final modeling frame and create hour-level time proxy for stable time split."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 16,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
